lead_paragraph: The New York police said the man was not considered a suspect or even a person of interest in the Aug. 2 killing of Karina Vetrano.

headline.print_headline: Police Release Sketch of Possible Witness in Queens Jogger’s Death
headline.main: Officials Release Sketch of Possible Witness in Queens Jogger’s Killing

snippet: The New York police said the man was not considered a suspect or even a person of interest in the Aug. 2 killing of Karina Vetrano....
abstract: New York City Police release sketch of man who was seen in area where jogger Karina Vetrano was strangled near her home in Queens; man could be witness with information about killing and police say he is not considered suspect or person of interest.
